{"tid":1659482,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大灣區 光復香港","createTime":"2019-10-17T03:30:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T03:30:30.000Z","uid":292456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"35fd6452264383beee18e93b1c92d245e7bbe4d6","tid":1659482,"uid":292456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T03:30:08.000Z","msg":"話說早兩日有大陸人打黎<br />\n(廣東話唔正）<br />\n估計係問我大灣區買唔買樓<br />\n<br />\n我就同佢講<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n叫佢跟住講 😨佢：咩話？<br />\n😊我：我教你講丫<br />\n😊：光～<br />\n😨：咩話？<br />\n😊：跟我講丫！光～<br />\n😨：光<br />\n😊：復～<br />\n😨：復<br />\n😊：光復香港<br />\n😨：光復中國？<br />\n😊：都得架、都得架😂<br />\n😊：時代革命<br />\n😨：時代革命共產黨<br />\n😊：光復中國、時代革命<br />\n😨：光復中國、時代革命共產黨<br />\n<br />\n跟住無啦啦鬧人垃圾<br />\n跟住收左線 😩賣樓不是這樣賣的～亲！<br />\n<br />\n提提大家10月20日<br />\n民陣大遊行<br />\n01:30pm<br />\n尖沙梳士巴利花園 遊行至 高鐵西九龍站<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4t7HZSE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4t7HZSE.png&h=68bae1e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0iSg4jk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0iSg4jk.jpg&h=60d0be08&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"423ffec70f16381f68f1f392a3f534210a7ab0d9","tid":1659482,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T03:30:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MHn4YGm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMHn4YGm.jpg&h=a9bf801a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"}]}